      <div class="msgContentFrame">Sell it? or, do the quest chain? <br /> <br />I was running FoS with guildies the other night, when Battered Hilt dropped. It was funny because we were all talking about how we never see it drop literally right before it dropped. I got lucky and won the roll. So, now I'm faced with the sell it or do the quest dilemna. <br /> <br />I have heard the quest line is really good, but I'm not really a lore-heavy type of player. I have read/heard people say it's one of the best in the game. I already have a better weapon, so it wouldn't be an upgrade. I'm a druid tank, btw. I have heard Battered hilt still sells for 7k gold, or thereabouts. It's tough to pass up that much gold, what with the upcoming gold sinks (training, professions, etc.) of Cata. <br /> <br />Just curious what others would do. <br /> <br />Thanks.</div>
